 # Commands
 
+## init
+
+Creates local data folders and writes `pala.config.json`.
+
+```text
+python pala.py init
+```
+
+Useful options:
+
+| Option | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--knowledge-bank C:\path\to\repo` | Default knowledge-bank repo path |
+| `--drive-target C:\path\to\Drive` | Default Drive-folder backup target |
+| `--mobile-share C:\path\to\folder` | Default phone/share sync folder |
+| `--dashboard-host 127.0.0.1` | Default dashboard host |
+| `--dashboard-port 8765` | Default dashboard port |
+| `--create-targets` | Create configured Drive/mobile folders |
+| `--force` | Overwrite existing config |
+
 ## remember
 
 Creates a local memory record as Markdown + JSON.
